419
00:26:12,404 --> 00:26:14,406
Jadi, jelas aku memercayainya.

420
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:18,619
Mereka USA Gymnastics.

421
00:26:18,702 --> 00:26:20,537
Ini Olimpiade AS.

422
00:26:30,798 --> 00:26:33,092
