01:27:16,898 --> 01:27:18,191
saling mendukung...

1450
01:27:18,650 --> 01:27:21,319
dan semangat pemberdayaan itu saja...

1451
01:27:22,654 --> 01:27:23,780
luar biasa.

1452
01:27:25,490 --> 01:27:27,576
Aku takkan lihat.
